<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA523_07_IH_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema523_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_07_ih_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="4" lang="y">주어진 도형이 점대칭도형이 아닌 이유를 써 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box align_center justify_center">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA523_07_IH/0004_01.png" alt="" />
          </div>
          <div class="input_area flex gap_10">
            <p class="label_reason">이유</p>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">
                  주어진 도형은 어떤 점을 중심으로 180° 돌렸을 때<br />
                  처음 도형과 완전히 겹치지 않습니다.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">점대칭도형은 대칭의 중심을 중심으로 180° 돌렸을 때 처음 도형과 완전히 겹칩니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
